Sci-fi adventure, starring Dwayne Johnson, AnnaSophia Robb, Alexander Ludwig and Carla Gugino.(n)

programme.title: Tron

Disney sci-fi adventure, starring Jeff Bridges, Bruce Boxleitner and David Warner.(n)
